storyinfo_16802=這大隊人馬是怎麼回事！？刑君可又在哪？上前詢問<a href="findnpc_new,city04,npc_hsp_mxm11" style="HLStype1">周立巍</a>
storyinfo_16803=那不是<a href="findnpc_new,city04,npc_hsp_mxm23" style="HLStype1">風堂主</a>嗎，果然快我一步
